sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant UI as React UI
    participant H as Custom Hooks
    participant SB as supabase-js
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant RT as Realtime Channel

    U->>UI: Drag task to "Done"
    UI->>H: updateTask(id, {status:"done"})
    H->>H: check_blocked_tasks RPC
    H-->>UI: Throw if blockers exist

    alt No blockers
        H->>SB: supabase.from('tasks').update(fields)
        SB->>PG: UPDATE tasks SET status='done'
        PG-->>SB: success
        SB-->>H: {data, error}
        H->>UI: Optimistic update (setTasks)

        PG->>RT: Broadcast change (channel 'board')
        RT-->>SB: postgres_changes event
        SB-->>H: payload received
        H->>PG: Re-fetch row with assignee join
        PG-->>H: enriched data
        H->>UI: Merge into task list

        U-->>U: Other client sees update instantly
    end
